{"tid":841914,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"人越大越開始覺得寧教人打仔莫教人分妻呢句野係戇撚鳩","createTime":"2018-09-30T00:41:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T01:24:06.000Z","uid":92376,"like":14,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c280aba0a1ffbbebcf8848099f81e65b26eec78d","tid":841914,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T00:41:12.000Z","msg":"現實根本係調返轉先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時一段關係要試到結埋婚相處過先唔夾<br />\n唔通仲要勉強繼續落去，喺呢個時候佢既好閨密或者死黨勸佢同老婆/老公離婚，又有咩錯先<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n相反打仔就唔好啦<br />\n先唔講犯法啦<br />\n時下啲細路比人打完<br />\n輕則嬲左父母以後仲難教<br />\n重則頂唔順自殺，現實都不時發生大把case<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以你地話寧教人打仔莫教人分妻呢句野係咪錯得離譜啦吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff286598d2a58d876d62a8c382d9fa58e66027ee","tid":841914,"uid":71913,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T00:43:28.000Z","msg":"係打仔同分妻都唔好理<br />\n<br />\n人地既家事理咁多做咩"},{"pid":"f04d736f2835dd07720201d6823be7ae9a1b43d0","tid":841914,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"ff286598d2a58d876d62a8c382d9fa58e66027ee","tid":841914,"uid":71913,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T00:43:28.000Z","msg":"係打仔同分妻都唔好理<br />\n<br />\n人地既家事理咁多做咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T00:44:10.000Z","msg":"討論重點係兩害取其輕，唔好講其他野thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"329318b8aab73780cebe92c3d90a790e3d35350b","tid":841914,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T00:45:01.000Z","msg":"天呀 仲以為今次會呃到正評<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">定其他人開呢個topic就會旺場 你地針對我想我死？</span>"},{"pid":"ae76a3b604d632187184de5ede47c2c270a08d09","tid":841914,"uid":68457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T00:49:54.000Z","msg":"召喚打老婆的老垃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b208ee5cb93f03a30833f730ab1da2a9e76d01b4","tid":841914,"uid":122556,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T01:08:51.000Z","msg":"可能離婚對個仔女影响仲大"},{"pid":"367e71bab2e96de26a63939a9efd950a1763f87d","tid":841914,"uid":173814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T01:15:19.000Z","msg":"on9<br />\n呢句野係話一家唔知一家事，你咪咁多爹。<br />\n另一個意義就係如果分唔成，結果咪你做醜人，仲自己無左個朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e553bc0694fdecfa0b4a0c929193ba7706b6f385","tid":841914,"uid":69528,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T01:16:42.000Z","msg":"要教人打仔，亦教人分妻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c08fcf1d2a6685dcb5baf47c94c47db86af57e2","tid":841914,"uid":187517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T01:24:06.000Z","msg":"反而覺得人大咗，所有嘢都有循環。公共利益要理，但私人事就唔好太過熱心"}]}